snippet.title: L'Oreal Is Getting Backlash For Praising Amber Heard In Recent Post
snippet.description:

Subscribe To InformOverload: http://bit.ly/2xB5CqA

The post was meant to celebrate women in cinema, but all it did was angery the justice for johnny depp army. I’ve got the tea and i’m gonna spill it, here for you on IO.
